\b0\f0\fs30 Trong b\f1\u7889?i c\u7843?nh th\u7871? gi\u7899?i hi\u7879?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?i \f2\'f0\f1\u7847?y bi\u7871?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng, vi\u7879?c t\f0\lang1033\'ecm hi\f1\lang1066\u7875?u v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f1\lang1066\u7913?ng d\u7909?ng nh\u7919?ng tri\u7871?t l\f0\lang1033\'fd c\f1\lang1066\u7893? x\f2\u432?a t\f1\u7915? \u7844?n \f2\'d0\f1\u7897? gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o kh\'f4ng ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? gi\f0\lang1033\'fap ch\'fang ta hi\f1\lang1066\u7875?u r\f0\lang1033\'f5 h\f2\u417?n v\f1\lang1066\u7873? m\u7897?t trong nh\u7919?ng t\f0\lang1033\'f4n gi\'e1o l\'e2u \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7901?i nh\u7845?t m\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\'f2n m\f1\lang1066\u7903? ra nh\u7919?ng gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? \f2\'f0\f1\u7841?o \f2\'f0\f1\u7913?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 tri th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? \f0\lang1033\'e1p d\f1\lang1066\u7909?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0o cu\f1\lang1066\u7897?c s\u7889?ng h\f0\lang1033\'e0ng ng\'e0y. B\'e0i vi\f1\lang1066\u7871?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0y s\f1\lang1066\u7869? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1m ph\'e1 c\'e1c nguy\'ean l\'fd c\f2\u417? b\f1\lang1066\u7843?n c\u7911?a \u7844?n \f2\'d0\f1\u7897? gi\f0\lang1033\'e1o, t\f1\lang1066\u7915? \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o n\u7873?n t\u7843?ng cho vi\u7879?c ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n t\f0\lang1033\'e2m h\f1\lang1066\u7891?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\'e0nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7897?ng \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'fang \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7855?n.\par
